This is an excellent, compact, and highly actionable cheat sheet! It is perfectly structured for immediate use and reinforces the core learning objective: AI is a tool that requires specific instructions to yield high-quality, professional results.
To "expand this cheat sheet a bit more" while maintaining its "one-page, fast-reference" utility, we will add sections that address the "Why" (The PUE link) and the "How-To" (The Curation skill), which are vital parts of your training.
Here is the expanded version in Bahasa Malaysia:
